C     -----------------------------------------------------------------
C
C*    COEFFICIENTS AND SECURITY PARAMETERS WITHIN *RADINT*
C
C CSDTSN :
C ZALBICE: FLOATING ICE ALBEDO
C ZALBSEA: OPEN SEA ALBEDO
C ZALBSNM:       SNOW ALBEDO
C ZALBSNO: THICK SNOW ALBEDO
C
C ZCARDI : SPECIFIC ATMOSPHERIC CONTENT IN CO2
C ZEMISS : SURFACE LONGWAVE EMISSIVITY
C
C ZSNOWAL: SNOW DEPTH (IN EQUIVALENT WATER) FOR WHICH SNOW IS CONSIDERED
C          AS THICK
C ZVLBDC : SPECIFIES THE REDUCTION OF THERMAL DIFFUSION UNDER VEGETATION
C ZEPALB : SECURITY TO AVOID ZERO ALBEDOS.
C ZEPCLC : SECURITY TO AVOID ZERO OR ONE CLOUD COVERS
C ZEPH2O : SECURITY TO AVOID WATER VAPOUR CONTENT IN A LAYER
C          TO BE MORE THEN THE RESPECTIVE VALUE AT SATURATION.
C ZEPSEC : AVOIDS 0/0 IN THE DIAGNOSTIC OF TOTAL CLOUD COVER.
C
      REAL ::       CSDTSN
     &             ,ZALBICE , ZALBSEA , ZALBSNM , ZALBSNO
     &             ,ZCARDI  , ZEMISS  , ZSNOWAL , ZVLBDC
     &             ,ZMETHA  , ZNITOX  , ZCFC(16)
     &             ,RCH4    , RN2O    , RCFC11  , RCFC12
     &             ,ZEPALB  , ZEPCLC  , ZEPH2O  , ZEPSEC
C
C
C
      COMMON/YOMRDI/CSDTSN
     &             ,ZALBICE , ZALBSEA , ZALBSNM , ZALBSNO
     &             ,ZCARDI  , ZEMISS  , ZSNOWAL , ZVLBDC
     &             ,ZMETHA  , ZNITOX  , ZCFC
     &             ,RCH4    , RN2O    , RCFC11  , RCFC12
     &             ,ZEPALB  , ZEPCLC  , ZEPH2O  , ZEPSEC
C     -----------------------------------------------------------------
